//
// Full-ELF event-trace design compiled through the --load-pdi-to-ctrl-pkt
// (control-packet) reconfigure flow. This exercises the compile path only.
//
// NOTE: at runtime this design hangs in this flow -- the trace shim DMA and the
// control-packet overlay contend for shim DMA resources -- so the kernel is not
// executed on hardware here. (The identical design without trace runs fine
// through --load-pdi-to-ctrl-pkt.) Compiling requires only peano.
//
// REQUIRES: peano
//
// RUN: %aiecc -v --get-full-elf --load-pdi-to-ctrl-pkt --no-xchesscc --no-xbridge %S/aie.mlir
